trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: Reprezentuje okno dialogowe, które umożliwia użytkownikowi wybieranie typu.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Ta klasa nie może być dziedziczona.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Ta klasa monituje użytkownika o przeglądać listę Windows Workflow Foundation i .NET Framework obszary nazw i typy zawarte i wybrać jednego typu.

trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"> </xref> przy użyciu <xref:System.IServiceProvider>, <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider"> </xref>, a ciąg.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.IServiceProvider>z którym usługi uzyskuje okna dialogowego.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: Gets the type selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera typ wybrane przez użytkownika w oknie dialogowym przeglądarki typu.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>Wybrane przez użytkownika w oknie dialogowym typu przeglądarki.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the component to associate with the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera składnik do skojarzenia z okna dialogowego typu przeglądarki.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli właściwość zwraca prawidłową wartość--innym niż odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic) — składnik jest dodawany do <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Ta właściwość jest wymagana, ponieważ <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementuje <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> always returns a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: Dla <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A>zawsze zwraca odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing`).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> to bind to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> to bind to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the container to associate with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera kontener do skojarzenia z okna dialogowego przeglądarki typu.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A> returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> has not bound an <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A>zwraca odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A>nie został powiązany <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent>do <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> </xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Component%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Ta metoda jest wymagane, ponieważ <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementuje <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Dla <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A>zawsze zwraca odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.Container%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera wartość wskazującą, czy okno dialogowe przeglądarki typu jest w trybie projektowania.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Ta właściwość jest wymagana, ponieważ <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementuje <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A> always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Dla <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A>zawsze zwraca `true`.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.ComponentModel.ISite.DesignMode%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"></xref> is in design mode; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Jeśli <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog"> </xref> jest w trybie projektowania; w przeciwnym razie <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Wartość domyślna to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera lub ustawia nazwę skojarzonego z okna dialogowego przeglądarki typu składnika.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Ta właściwość jest wymagana, ponieważ <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>implementuje <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>

trans-unit.source: The name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Nazwa składnika skojarzone z okna dialogowego przeglądarki typu.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera obiekt usługi określonego typu.

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli `serviceType` jest typu <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>zwraca obiekt usługi.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A> returns a null reference (`Nothing`).
trans-unit.target: W przeciwnym razie <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>zwraca odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing`).</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System.IServiceProvider.GetService%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of service object to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>Obiektu usługi do pobrania.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A service object of type serviceType, or a null reference ( in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type serviceType.
trans-unit.target: Obiekt usługi typu serviceType , lub odwołanie o wartości null ( w języku Visual Basic), jeśli nie ma żadnego obiektu usługi typu serviceType .
